dct_title_s: Bound Brook & Bloomington, Somerset Co., N. J. (Sheet 2)
dct_description_sm: "July 1890." Includes key, key map and text. "3890". The name of South Bound Brook was changed to Bloomington in 1869. In 1891, the name reverted back to South Bound Brook. cf. Wikipedia.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn-Perris Map Co., Limited, 1890.

dcat_theme_sm: Fire insurance maps—New Jersey—South Bound Brook—1890
